title: How to stay on your 24 hour plan
itunes:title: How to stay on your 24 hour plan
description:
Get the Free Course here:
https://phit.click/freecourse

 

In this episode we go a little deeper into how to create a realistic 24 hour plan.

Episode 023: The 24 Hour Planning Rule to Get Back on Track gives you the basics of the plan. Today's episode gives you tips on writing a plan that you can commit to and execute.

I coach so many girls on why they don't stay on plan. And most of the time it's because they've created an unrealistic plan.

Today you'll learn how to meet yourself where you are, plan in a way you can execute, and level up in small steps.
